**Overview**

This dashboard is a health overview related to the ThreatQ integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the health of the ingestion of indicators from ThreatQ.

It shows the ingestion rates (by default it fetches new updates every 10 minutes) and provides a few filters for drilling down to specific indicator types retrieved from ThreatQ.
